      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a rigorous showroom standard that will satisfy the most exacting collector. Every detail of this automobile reflects an uncompromising commitment to preservation, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior cabin. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen defined by peerless mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. Inspections by appointment only.",
