      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute dream of a car. It has been totally babied since day one\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a single blemish on it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that\u2019s been cared for with love, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
