    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a superlative 996.2 GT3, featuring the legendary 3.6L Mezger flat-six power unit with a motorsport-derived dry-sump lubrication system. This high-revving atmospheric engine delivers linear power through a G96/96 six-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is strictly original, retaining its adjustable coilover suspension and four-piston monoblock calipers. Meticulously maintained with zero evidence of RMS weeping or bore scoring, the vehicle presents in concours-level condition. The original paint exhibits perfect depth, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or delamination. A turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
