      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the factory 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component, switch, and gauge functions exactly as it did the moment it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. This sale includes all original documentation, the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is the one.",
